{"type": "article", "id": 12172, "title": "“Zero 1”系列音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145946FhYg9HRm1dODyLGQ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国音响公司 Avantgarde Acoustic 公司推出了一款全新的音箱 “Zero 1” 系列，音箱外形时尚现代，采用经典的凹型球面波喇叭，每一只喇叭都由一个50瓦的功率放大器驱动。而每个音箱里面都有一个 400 瓦的低音功率放大器，扬声器之间的连接采用了无线连接方式，音质不受音箱位置的变化而受影响，音压可以达到 104dB 以上。<a href=\"http://www.avantgarde-acoustic.de/home.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400096jI9kiPqmGWar8TF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140011XV2F5CrHEhxOqA6e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140011CHRB8uUIKQjdxYDk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43398533\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400126zXOJ3s9uvhZTQAU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}